ruby程序中 使用ARGV这个预定好数组来获取命令行传递的数据
如：print_argv.rb
puts "first argv : #{ARGV[0]}"
puts "2 argv : #{ARGV[1]}"
puts "3 argv : #{ARGV[2]}"
输出
D:\evenote_ruby\note\codes>ruby print_argv.rb 1st 2nd 3rd
first argv : 1st
2 argv : 2nd
3 argv : 3rd

如：happy_birth.rb
name = ARGV[0]
print "Happy Birthday, " , name ,"!\n"
D:\evenote_ruby\note\codes>ruby happy_birth.rb tony
Happy Birthday, tony!
